summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing the employment of Worthington-Christiani-Fenco for engineering services in connection with the R. H. Thomson Expressway Union Bay undercrossing and the execution of such agreement as may be necessary to obtain 50% reimbursement from the State of expenditures made in connection therewith and making an appropriation from the Seattle General Street Improvement Bonds 1960 Fund therefor.
